## Imported Files
## ${CAPA_Tools}Problem
## ${CAPA_GraphicsDirectory}Gtype10/prob12.eps
## Values needing defined:
## prob_val (number, e.g. /LET prob_val=1)
## prob_try (number, e.g. /LET prob_try=5)
## 
